An Honest Assessment
THE HARD TRUTH
10K signals in 30 days as a solo founder with $0 budget is in the top 1% of OSS launch outcomes. Paperclip did 30K in 21 days, but Paperclip had: perfect timing (multi-agent hype cycle peaking), a working product with immediate visual demo (React dashboard), and arguably the most viral framing in the AI agent space. SupraWall is a security tool — security tools are harder to make viral because the pain is latent (you don't know you need a firewall until you get hacked). This plan is designed to overcome that by making the pain visible through content. If you execute every single day, the conservative math gets you to 9,000. One breakout event (HN front page, GitHub Trending, or a viral tweet) pushes you past 10K. The plan creates enough surface area that at least one breakout is statistically likely.

The order matters. The daily rhythm matters. The narrative consistency matters. Skip nothing, and let compounding do the rest.
